@namespace PgmStudio.Client.Pages.AuthoringParts
@using PgmStudio.Client.Pages.EditorActivities

@* Wools (04) — four sub-steps: Colours, Spawn, Monuments, Room. Each a full workspace; the flow bar is
   separate from the canvas toolbar; Back/Next on every step. Each inspector shows only the active step's
   region. The sidebar list's leading mark + header reflect the region authored this step: colours = colour
   swatch, spawn = point icon, monuments = block icon, room = rectangle icon (all team-coloured). Canvas =
   thunder's REAL islands faint for context + the real wool spawns / monuments / rooms. Room is last and
   carries the auto-wiring summary. *@

<section class="ds-section" id="wools">
  <div class="ds-section-heading">
    <div>
      <p class="ds-kicker">04</p>
      <h2>Wools</h2>
    </div>
    <p>Four sub-steps — colours, then the wool spawn, then the monuments, then the room. Define one wool
       unit; orbit-fill produces the other three. N − 1 = 3 monuments per wool on a four-team map.</p>
  </div>

  <p class="ds-theming-note">
    A <em>wool unit</em> is one coloured wool block, the room it lives in, and the capture monuments that
    record each enemy team's take. Author only the blue wool; <code>rot_90</code> symmetry orbit-fills
    green, red, and yellow. Room defense, room build/break, and monument capture are auto-wired from
    templates — you never touch the filter graph. Splitting spawn, monuments, and room into their own
    steps keeps each inspector focused on one region.
  </p>

  <div class="ds-sug-sample" style="max-width:340px;margin:var(--space-4) 0">
    <SmartSuggestion Header="Smart Suggestion" Badge="4 teams" AcceptLabel="Pre-fill 3 monuments" RejectLabel="Dismiss">
      <p class="smart-suggestion__text">Four teams means each wool must be captured by every other team — three monuments per wool.</p>
      <div class="smart-suggestion-teams">
        <div class="smart-suggestion-team"><span class="list-swatch list-swatch--sm" style="background:#55FF55"></span>Green</div>
        <div class="smart-suggestion-team"><span class="list-swatch list-swatch--sm" style="background:#FF5555"></span>Red</div>
        <div class="smart-suggestion-team"><span class="list-swatch list-swatch--sm" style="background:#FFFF55"></span>Yellow</div>
        <div class="smart-suggestion-team"></div>
      </div>
    </SmartSuggestion>
  </div>

  <div class="ds-steps">

  @* ── Step 1 · Colours (sidebar: colour swatches) ───────────────────────── *@
  <article class="ds-example">
    <div class="ds-example-label">Step 1 of 4 — Colours</div>
    <div class="flow-bar">
      <div class="flow-steps">
        <button class="flow-step flow-step--active">Colours</button>
        <button class="flow-step">Spawn</button>
        <button class="flow-step">Monuments</button>
        <button class="flow-step">Room</button>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-bar-actions">
        <button class="action-btn" disabled>Back</button>
        <button class="action-btn action-btn--primary">Next: Spawn</button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="ds-workspace-frame">
      <div class="workspace">
        <div class="workspace-sidebar">
          <div class="workspace-scroll">
            <section class="panel-section">
              <div class="section-header section-header--ruled"><h2 class="section-title">Wools</h2></div>
              <div class="panel-list">
                <div class="list-row list-row--compact list-row--selected"><span class="list-swatch" style="background:#5555FF"></span><span class="list-label list-label--mono">blue-wool</span><span class="badge badge--success">authored</span></div>
                <div class="list-row list-row--compact"><span class="list-swatch" style="background:#55FF55"></span><span class="list-label list-label--mono">green-wool</span><span class="badge badge--dim">orbit</span></div>
                <div class="list-row list-row--compact"><span class="list-swatch" style="background:#FF5555"></span><span class="list-label list-label--mono">red-wool</span><span class="badge badge--dim">orbit</span></div>
                <div class="list-row list-row--compact"><span class="list-swatch" style="background:#FFFF55"></span><span class="list-label list-label--mono">yellow-wool</span><span class="badge badge--dim">orbit</span></div>
              </div>
            </section>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sidebar-handle"></div>
        <div class="workspace-canvas">
          <div class="canvas-subbar">
            <div class="canvas-toolbar">
              <button class="draw-tool-btn draw-tool-btn--active" title="Pan"><i data-lucide="hand"></i></button>
              <button class="draw-tool-btn" title="Select"><i data-lucide="mouse-pointer-2"></i></button>
            </div>
            <div class="subbar-sep"></div>
            <button class="filter-chip filter-chip--active" title="Orbit fill active">Orbit</button>
            <span class="canvas-cursor">X -112 · Z 8</span>
            <div class="canvas-subbar-right">
              <button class="draw-tool-btn" title="Fit island"><i data-lucide="maximize-2"></i></button>
              <button class="draw-tool-btn" title="Reset zoom"><i data-lucide="scan"></i></button>
              <span class="canvas-zoom">100%</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="canvas-surface canvas-surface--svg">
            <IslandMap Mode="neutral">
              <circle cx="15.5" cy="136.5" r="2.6" fill="#5555FF" stroke="white" stroke-width="0.7" />
              <circle cx="241.5" cy="120.5" r="2.4" fill="#55FF55" stroke="white" stroke-width="0.5" opacity="0.6" />
              <circle cx="136.5" cy="241.5" r="2.4" fill="#FF5555" stroke="white" stroke-width="0.5" opacity="0.6" />
              <circle cx="120.5" cy="15.5" r="2.4" fill="#FFFF55" stroke="white" stroke-width="0.5" opacity="0.6" />
            </IslandMap>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sidebar-handle"></div>
        <div class="workspace-inspector">
          <div class="workspace-scroll">
            <section class="panel-section">
              <div class="detail-header">
                <span class="geo-type-icon detail-icon--muted"><i data-lucide="square"></i></span>
                <span class="detail-label detail-label--mono">blue-wool</span>
                <span class="badge badge--neutral">Wool</span>
              </div>
              <div class="section-body">
                <div class="field"><label class="field-label">Colour</label><div class="field-pick-row"><span class="field-swatch" style="background:#5555FF"></span><select class="field-input"><option selected>Blue</option></select></div></div>
                <div class="field"><label class="field-label">Owning team</label><div class="field-pick-row"><span class="field-swatch" style="background:#5555FF"></span><select class="field-input"><option selected>Blue</option><option>Green</option><option>Red</option><option>Yellow</option></select></div></div>
                <p class="section-desc">Pick the authored wool's colour. Orbit assigns green, red, and yellow by 90° rotation.</p>
              </div>
            </section>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

