    @* Smart-detect path — backend = MonumentSuggester (docs/contracts/monument-suggestion.md). Instead of
       placing each monument by hand, the author BOXES one monument cluster and declares its SCHEMATIC —
       pedestal (block below) × label (sign / armour stand / none) × cap (block above) — and the world scan
       returns ranked ghost suggestions (inferred wool colour + confidence + evidence) to confirm/dismiss.
       Grounded in REAL thunder: green's cluster (blue-green/red-green/yellow-green at x71-73, z18, y8) reads
       as bedrock pedestal + "<colour> Wool monument" sign below + open cap → 3 sign hits at conf 0.90,
       colours blue/red/yellow (verified: tools/PgmStudio.RoundTrip --suggest-monuments thunder). *@
    <p class="ds-theming-note" style="margin-top:var(--space-5)">
      <em>Or — smart-detect from the world.</em> Rather than placing each monument by hand, box one
      monument cluster and declare its <em>schematic</em>: the <em>pedestal</em> below, the <em>label</em>
      (sign, armour stand, or none) and the <em>cap</em> above. The world scan reads the built blocks and
      returns ranked ghost suggestions — each with an inferred wool colour, a confidence, and the evidence
      it came from — to confirm or dismiss. Backend: <code>MonumentSuggester</code>
      (<code>docs/contracts/monument-suggestion.md</code>).
    </p>

    <div class="ds-example-label">Smart-detect — box the cluster, declare the schematic</div>
    <div class="ds-workspace-frame">
      <div class="workspace">
        @* SIDEBAR · the schematic picker (the "which monument style?" menu) + ranked suggestions *@
        <div class="workspace-sidebar">
          <div class="workspace-scroll">
            <div class="panel-stack">
              <section class="panel-section">
                <div class="section-header section-header--ruled">
                  <h2 class="section-title">Monument schematic</h2>
                  <span class="badge badge--neutral">green cluster</span>
                </div>
                <div class="section-body">
                  <div class="field">
                    <label class="field-label">Signature <span class="text-muted text-sm">(below · monument · above)</span></label>
                    <div class="canvas-surface canvas-surface--svg" style="height:130px;border-radius:var(--radius-sm)">
                      <svg viewBox="0 0 150 126" style="width:100%;height:100%">
                        @* cap · open (air) — dashed empty cell above *@
                        <rect x="46" y="8" width="42" height="30" rx="1.5" fill="none" stroke="var(--canvas-axis)" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="3 2"/>
                        <text x="94" y="27" fill="var(--text-muted)" font-size="9" font-family="ui-monospace,monospace">open</text>
                        @* monument cell — air, the wool goes here (ghost) *@
                        <rect x="46" y="40" width="42" height="30" rx="1.5" fill="color-mix(in oklch,#5555FF 16%,transparent)" stroke="#5555FF" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="3 2"/>
                        <rect x="58" y="47" width="18" height="16" rx="1.5" fill="#5555FF"/>
                        <text x="94" y="59" fill="var(--text-secondary)" font-size="9" font-family="ui-monospace,monospace">wool</text>
                        @* pedestal · bedrock — solid cell below *@
                        <rect x="46" y="72" width="42" height="30" rx="1.5" fill="#33363d" stroke="var(--border)" stroke-width="1"/>
                        <text x="94" y="91" fill="var(--text-muted)" font-size="9" font-family="ui-monospace,monospace">bedrock</text>
                        @* sign below — beside the pedestal, facing the monument *@
                        <rect x="10" y="76" width="26" height="16" rx="1.5" fill="#6b4f2a" stroke="#3f2f19" stroke-width="0.8"/>
                        <line x1="14" y1="81" x2="32" y2="81" stroke="#d8c9a8" stroke-width="1.1"/>
                        <line x1="14" y1="86" x2="28" y2="86" stroke="#d8c9a8" stroke-width="1.1"/>
                        <text x="10" y="110" fill="var(--text-muted)" font-size="8" font-family="ui-monospace,monospace">sign · below</text>
                      </svg>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="field"><label class="field-label">Pedestal · below</label><select class="field-input"><option>Any</option><option selected>Bedrock</option><option>Stained clay</option><option>Stained glass</option><option>Wool</option><option>Floating</option></select></div>
                  <div class="field"><label class="field-label">Label</label><select class="field-input"><option>Any</option><option selected>Sign below</option><option>Sign above</option><option>Armour stand</option><option>None</option></select></div>
                  <div class="field"><label class="field-label">Cap · above</label><select class="field-input"><option>Any</option><option selected>Open (air)</option><option>Stained glass</option><option>Stained clay</option><option>Bedrock</option><option>Slab</option><option>Barrier</option><option>Wool</option><option>Sign</option></select></div>
                  <div class="field"><label class="field-label">Boxed area <span class="text-muted text-sm">(world)</span></label><div class="field-value">X 62‥84 · Y 0‥16 · Z 8‥28</div></div>
                  <button class="action-btn action-btn--primary action-btn--full action-btn--separated"><i data-lucide="scan-search"></i> Detect monuments</button>
                  <p class="section-desc">3 found · all sign-labelled · 0 dismissed.</p>
                </div>
              </section>
              <section class="panel-section">
                <div class="section-header section-header--ruled">
                  <h2 class="section-title">Suggestions</h2>
                  <span class="badge badge--dim">3 in box</span>
                </div>
                <div class="panel-list">
                  <div class="list-row list-row--compact list-row--selected"><span class="list-swatch" style="background:#5555FF"></span><span class="list-label list-label--mono">blue-green</span><span class="badge badge--success">0.90</span></div>
                  <div class="list-row list-row--compact"><span class="list-swatch" style="background:#FF5555"></span><span class="list-label list-label--mono">red-green</span><span class="badge badge--success">0.90</span></div>
                  <div class="list-row list-row--compact"><span class="list-swatch" style="background:#FFFF55"></span><span class="list-label list-label--mono">yellow-green</span><span class="badge badge--success">0.90</span></div>
                </div>
                <p class="section-desc">Ranked highest-confidence first. A stained pedestal/cap would set the colour directly; here the sign text does. Low-confidence geometry hits would appear muted.</p>
